ed out."],[3978,4049,"Amnesia."],[4079,4187,"Thank fucking God."],[4250,4320,"She doesn't remember"],[4320,4441,"that I burned her to death."],[4450,4625,"And why is Brian with some girl"],[4625,4758,"that looks exactly like me?"],[4813,4967,"I knew that other bitch was a fraud."],[5059,5171,"Time to take her down."],[5267,5401,"There was this terrible fire,"],[5451,5576,"and you got really burnt up."],[5689,5860,"And that, that demon girl up there,"],[5860,5960,"she's behind all of it."],[6006,6181,"She kicked me out of Ramma Phi and,"],[6181,6439,"and left me bloody down here to die."],[6464,6523,"What?"],[6669,6802,"Why is Brian with her?"],[6861,7032,"Because he's thinking with his dick"],[7032,7190,"and she's manipulative."],[7190,7344,"She's, she's got him in this grasp."],[7344,7503,"She's really dangerous."],[7507,7574,"Oh my God."],[7699,7816,"No one believes I'm me."],[7899,8045,"What if she tries to hurt Brian?"],[8070,8149,"No, hey, hey."],[8149,8254,"Don't worry about it, okay?"],[8375,8550,"Don't worry because we can fix this."],[8608,8767,"At the Sorority Ball tomorrow night,"],[8787,8913,"everyone's going to be there, and,"],[9000,9084,"and you can stand up and"],[9084,9192,"expose that fraud."],[9255,9530,"But I'm not a Ramma."],[9642,9822,"I never completed the crossing."],[9822,9922,"They won't let me in."],[10039,10139,"It's okay, Little."],[10239,10318,"I'll get you in."],[10648,10756,"Thank you."],[10919,11144,"I'd be lost without you, Mickey."],[11173,11319,"This seems more like Ashlyn."],[11390,11644,"So naive and easy to control."],[11732,11790,"Once we deal with"],[11790,11886,"this imposter problem,"],[11886,11995,"I'll get rid of her for good."]],"38":[[346,458,"I can't wait to announce you"],[458,629,"as president of my charity at the ball."],[1155,1313,"You and I,"],[1313,1438,"we're unstoppable."],[1822,1906,"I have a gift for you."],[2398,2506,"Oh, you shouldn't have."],[2577,2619,"Are,"],[2727,2869,"are these the limited edition shoes"],[2869,2965,"I was telling you about?"],[2998,3161,"They are like $15,000."],[3265,3353,"Once I steal all the"],[3353,3495,"rest of Ashlyn's inheritance,"],[3511,3624,"I can dump this bitch"],[3624,3787,"and buy all the shoes I want."],[3858,3995,"He still thinks he can win."],[4062,4245,"He thinks he can get whatever he wants."],[4358,4558,"She has no idea what I'm capable of."],[4596,4696,"She has no idea"],[4696,4833,"what's coming to her next."],[5284,5330,"Oh!"]],"39":[[25,129,"Oh!"],[129,233,"What the hell is this?"],[321,450,"Does it remind you of anything?"],[1209,1418,"Relax, I'm just joking."],[1455,1568,"What did Mckenna tell you?"],[1801,1851,"Did,"],[1922,2147,"did you remember something?"],[2248,2318,"No."],[2431,2485,"Why? Are,"],[2540,2706,"are you feeling guilty about something?"],[2731,2827,"No, I'm just,"],[2907,2982,"I'm just excited"],[2982,3078,"to get into the meat of the work,"],[3078,3148,"you know. I,"],[3203,3332,"I'd do anything to help people."],[3428,3524,"More like anything"],[3524,3649,"to get my hands on your money."],[3724,3870,"That's why you're my president."],[6272,6356,"You wanna dance?"],[6423,6502,"Tonight's the night."],[6769,6865,"You want to be a Ramma, right?"],[7620,7728,"The Wadsworth fortune is"],[7728,7811,"almost mine."]],"40":[[971,1142,"If he hadn't burned my sister alive"],[1142,1209,"for her money,"],[1226,1347,"he'd almost be charming."],[1363,1463,"You've got everything coming"],[1463,1584,"for you, baby."],[1780,1881,"Hey, yo!"],[1893,2081,"Welcome to the Sorority Ball, ya'll."],[2081,2273,"Let's make some noise."],[2469,2669,"My Greek family recently experienced"],[2669,2831,"a horrible tragedy."],[2844,2998,"A pledge was trapped in a fire"],[2998,3128,"and almost died."],[3136,3307,"But somehow she survived"],[3332,3507,"and is alive and here today."],[3578,3720,"Welcome our survivor,"],[3720,3941,"our Sorority Games Champ,"],[3987,4154,"and the first ever President"],[4179,4346,"of Ramma Phi,"],[4371,4675,"Ashlyn Wadsworth!"]],"41":[[0,158,"Thank you all for being here tonight."],[204,429,"As many of you know, my father"],[429,596,"left me with billions,"],[596,788,"and I've been thinking about,"],[850,959,"what I wanna do with it."],[1001,1255,"Tonight, I want to officially announce,"],[1322,1405,"my new charity,"],[1476,1664,"The Wadsworth Cares Initiative."],[1801,1906,"Woo-hoo!"],[2293,2364,"Thank you."],[2464,2615,"Ashlyn Wadsworth, everyone."],[2644,2681,"All right,"],[2681,2802,"I just wanna say a couple words."],[2840,2948,"I am so proud,"],[2994,3169,"of Ashlyn for funding something"],[3169,3278,"she truly believes in."],[3278,3486,"The Wadsworth Cares Initiative,"],[3516,3670,"can help girls everywhere."],[3795,4124,"But only if Ashlyn faces the truth."],[4175,4354,"She is still a raging alcoholic"],[4354,4537,"and unfit to lead the charity."]],"42":[[8,196,"You know, after the accident,"],[196,279,"you're still drinking,"],[279,408,"and you're still hurting others,"],[408,508,"and you're still hurting yourself,"],[508,658,"and you don't even care."],[1105,1155,"Look at that."],[1701,1897,"Ashlyn, I'm worried about you."],[1951,2060,"You can't run a charity"],[2060,2298,"when you yourself need the help."],[2306,2565,"These photos, my sister didn't do this."],[2727,2823,"Brian did this to her."],[2848,2994,"He and her backstabbing bestie,"],[2994,3048,"Mckenna."],[3319,3465,"When you drink, Ashlyn,"],[3549,3628,"you get mean,"],[3645,3757,"and sometimes you hit me."],[3853,3933,"And it hurts."],[4041,4216,"It hurts, not just literally,"],[4270,4346,"but in here."],[4667,4813,"This is so toxic."],[4863,4913,"So Ash,"],[4913,5096,"if you can't see that you need help,"],[5159,5284,"I don't know what type of future"],[5284,5359,"you think we have."],[5363,5593,"What the fuck do you want, Brian?"],[5647,5784,"You said you wanted me to run"],[5784,5876,"Wadsworth Cares."],[5901,6022,"Keep you word and step down."],[6243,6306,"You know what?"],[6335,6473,"He has no idea what's coming."],[6514,6573,"You're right."]],"43":[[79,125,"You're right."],[337,479,"Of course I'm right, baby."],[546,754,"Everyone, Brian is amazing."],[754,975,"I think he should be president,"],[1276,1501,"of The Wadsworth Cares Initiative."],[1559,1664,"Let's make it official."],[1701,1826,"Now I'm so rich,"],[1826,1976,"the law can't even touch me."],[3023,3136,"Thank you so much for this."],[3199,3269,"But uh,"],[3299,3390,"it's over between us."],[3478,3574,"I'm breaking up with you!"],[3953,3999,"Yeah, that's right,"],[3999,4083,"I'm breaking up with you."],[4095,4225,"You know, ever since the accident,"],[4237,4341,"you're just like a different person,"],[4341,4396,"you know?"],[4454,4587,"It's not the girl I fell in love with."],[4612,4708,"Okay, so you think"],[4708,4950,"that I exist for your benefit?"],[4979,5113,"You know, as you all may know,"],[5113,5321,"Brian wants to be the president someday."],[5413,5584,"I really think that he could do it."],[5730,5789,"Unless..."],[6339,6489,"These photos somehow,"],[6539,6606,"get leaked."],[7065,7152,"Shit."]],"44":[[467,579,"You know, that's very funny."],[588,750,"It's, that's very funny, because did you,"],[800,892,"were you drunk when you"],[892,1001,"AI generated this?"],[1059,1309,"That, that looks nothing like me."],[1351,1422,"Look, you know,"],[1422,1593,"this just leads me to my next point,"],[1614,1760,"that she is not fit"],[1772,1997,"to lead The Wadsworth Cares!"],[1997,2173,"Speaking of, on my first day,"],[2206,2298,"I plan to allocate"],[2298,2427,"for all struggling students,"],[2444,2552,"here at SMU."],[2740,2911,"Yo, how the fuck does she have this?"],[3132,3232,"Wait, what are you doing?"],[3428,3507,"This is what I'm doing."],[3574,3628,"Um that?"],[3657,3762,"That is clearly fake."],[3924,4049,"Oh yeah,"],[4049,4237,"drink that piss, you little chickie!"],[4779,4971,"That is obviously a deepfake."],[5009,5201,"She is just doing this because she's mad,"],[5201,5334,"because I 